7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Bito AI and Codium AI share a solid foundation of core features including Code Review, Debugging, Test Generation, Multi Language. Where Bito AI pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Autocomplete and Code Generation and Refactoring and Chat and Documentation, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Bito AI holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Codium AI scores 7/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Bito AI offers a more budget-friendly entry point at $15/mo, compared to Codium AI's starting price of $19/mo. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Bito AI's free tier and Codium AI's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
